721560","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/9877","id":1156721560,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAjwLdc5E8iuY","user":{"login":"EmptyRabbit","id":32815055,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMyODE1MDU1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/32815055?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit","html_url":"https://github.com/EmptyRabbit","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-06-15T17:04:34Z","updated_at":"2022-06-15T17:06:23Z","body":"I would like to fix this issue\r\n\r\nIt seems that when setup/call/teardown stage begin, will init a stage log records stash, which used in `LogCaptureFixture.get_records`,\r\nbut after `LogCaptureFixture.clear`, the stage records in stash not be reset\r\n\r\nI tried to fix with the following changed\r\n```python\r\n# _pytest/logging.py\r\ndef _runtest_for(self, item: nodes.Item, when: str) -> Generator[None, None, None]:\r\n    \"\"\"Implement the internals of the pytest_runtest_xxx() hooks.\"\"\"\r\n    with catching_logs(\r\n            self.caplog_handler,\r\n            level=self.log_level,\r\n    ) as caplog_handler, catching_logs(\r\n        self.report_handler,\r\n        level=self.log_level,\r\n    ) as report_handler:\r\n        caplog_handler.reset()\r\n        caplog_handler.set_when(when)  # Add \"when\" property to LogCaptureHandler, set stage in runtest\r\n        report_handler.reset()\r\n        item.stash[caplog_records_key][when] = caplog_handler.records\r\n        item.stash[caplog_handler_key] = caplog_handler\r\n\r\n        yield\r\n\r\n        log = report_handler.stream.getvalue().strip()\r\n        item.add_report_section(when, \"log\", log)\r\n\r\n```\r\n```python\r\n# _pytest/logging.py\r\ndef clear(self) -> None:\r\n    \"\"\"Reset the list of log records and the captured log text.\"\"\"\r\n    self.handler.reset()\r\n    self._item.stash[caplog_records_key][self.handler.when] = self.records    # consistent with records after clear\r\n```","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/comments/1156721560/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"EmptyRabbit","id":32815055,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMyODE1MDU1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/32815055?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit","html_url":"https://github.com/EmptyRabbit","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EmptyRabbit/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":6814788739,"node_id":"REFE_lADOAjwLdc5IML4OzwAA